{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"bannerSample.jpg","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"해당 문서는 UIKit 사용자를 위한 문서이며, SwiftUI 사용자는 다른 문서를 참고하시길 바랍니다."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"1. 광고 요청하기","level":2,"anchor":"1-%EA%B4%91%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0","type":"heading"},{"tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import UIKit","import AdFitSDK","","class MyViewController: UIViewController {","","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","        let bannerAdView = AdFitBannerAdView(clientId: \"Input Your ClientId\", adUnitSize: \"320x50\")","        bannerAdView.frame = CGRect(x: 0, y: 0, width: view.bounds.width, height: 50)","        bannerAdView.rootViewController = self","        view.addSubview(bannerAdView)","        bannerAdView.loadAd()","    }","","}"]}],"title":"Swift"},{"title":"Objective C","content":[{"code":["#import \"MyViewController.h\"","#import <AdFit\/AdFit-Swift.h>","","@implementation MyViewController","","- (void)viewDidLoad {","    [super viewDidLoad];","    AdFitBannerAdView *bannerAdView = [[AdFitBannerAdView alloc] initWithClientId:@\"Input Your ClientId\" ","                                                                       adUnitSize:@\"320x50\"];","    bannerAdView.frame = CGRectMake(0.f, 0.f, self.view.bounds.size.width, 50.f);","    bannerAdView.rootViewController = self;","    [self.view addSubview:bannerAdView];","    [bannerAdView loadAd];","}","","@end"],"syntax":"objc","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"text":"2. 배너 속성 설정","anchor":"2-%EB%B0%B0%EB%84%88-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95","type":"heading","level":2},{"text":"1) rootViewController","anchor":"1-rootViewController","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"배너 광고 클릭 시, AdFit SDK에 포함된 웹뷰 컨트롤러가 modal 방식으로 나타나며 광고주 페이지가 노출됩니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"이때 AdFit SDK는 내부적으로 적절한 뷰 컨트롤러를 탐색한 후, 탐색된 뷰 컨트롤러를 통해 광고주 페이지를 노출시킵니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"광고주 페이지를 노출시킬 뷰 컨트롤러를 직접 지정하고자 하는 경우, 해당 뷰 컨트롤러 객체를 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" 프로퍼티에 할당해 주세요."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"2) delegate","anchor":"2-delegate","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"배너 광고로부터 발생하는 특정 이벤트를 감지하기 위해, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"delegate"},{"type":"text","text":" 프로퍼티를 활용할 수 있습니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AdFitBannerAdViewDelegate"},{"text":" 프로토콜을 구현한 클래스의 객체를 ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"delegate"},{"type":"text","text":" 프로퍼티에 할당해 주면 됩니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"자세한 사항은 "},{"identifier":"#heading3","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" 항목을 참고해 주세요."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"3. delegate 메서드 구현","anchor":"3-delegate-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%9C%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84","type":"heading","level":2},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"AdFitBannerAdViewDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" 프로토콜을 구현함으로써 광고로부터 발생하는 특정 이벤트를 감지할 수 있습니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"광고를 정상적으로 받은 경우, 광고를 받지 못한 경우, 광고가 클릭된 경우에 대한 delegate 메서드를 제공합니다.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"tabs":[{"title":"Swift","content":[{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func adViewDidReceiveAd(_ bannerAdView: AdFitBannerAdView) {","    print(\"didReceiveAd\")","}","    ","func adViewDidFailToReceiveAd(_ bannerAdView: AdFitBannerAdView, error: Error) {","    print(\"didFailToReceiveAd - error :\\(error.localizedDescription)\")","}","    ","func adViewDidClickAd(_ bannerAdView: AdFitBannerAdView) {","    print(\"didClickAd\")","}"]}]},{"title":"Objective C","content":[{"code":["- (void)adViewDidReceiveAd:(AdFitBannerAdView *)bannerAdView {","    NSLog(@\"didReceiveAd\");","}","","- (void)adViewDidFailToReceiveAd:(AdFitBannerAdView *)bannerAdView error:(NSError *)error {","    NSLog(@\"didFailToReceiveAd - error = %@\", [error localizedDescription]);","}","","- (void)adViewDidClickAd:(AdFitBannerAdView *)bannerAdView {","    NSLog(@\"didClickAd\");","}"],"syntax":"objc","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"text":"4. 에러 코드","anchor":"4-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"광고 수신에 실패한 경우, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"adViewDidFailToReceiveAd"},{"text":" delegate 메서드를 통해 에러 객체를 전달받을 수 있습니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"각각의 에러에 대한 설명은 아래 표를 참고해 주세요.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"코드"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"메시지","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"설명"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"clientId property is nil","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"AdFitBannerAdView 객체에 clientId가 세팅되지 않은 경우."}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"2","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"no ad to show"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"노출 가능한 광고가 없는 경우. 잠시 후 다시 광고 요청을 시도해 주세요.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"3","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"invalid ad received"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"유효하지 않은 광고를 받은 경우. AdFit에 문의해 주세요.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"4"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"failed to render ad","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"AdFitBannerAdView 객체의 사이즈가 기준 사이즈보다 작은 경우.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"5"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"attempted to load ad too frequently","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"과도하게 짧은 시간 간격(30초 이내)으로 광고를 재요청한 경우.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"6"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP failed"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"HTTP 에러. 계속해서 반복 발생하는 경우 AdFit에 문의해 주세요.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"14"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"failed to load webview"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"인앱 브라우저 내의 광고의 로딩을 실패했을 경우."}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","alignments":["center","unset","unset"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/BannerAd","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"광고 연동","identifiers":["doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/NativeAd","doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/popUp","doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/BizBoardTemplate","doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/Simple+SwiftUI","doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK\/NativeAdIntroduce"],"generated":true,"anchor":"광고-연동"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/adfitsdk\/bannerad"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"배너 광고 연동 과정을 소개합니다."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"title":"배너 광고 연동","modules":[{"name":"AdFitSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","images":[{"identifier":"banner-card.png","type":"card"},{"identifier":"iphone.png","type":"icon"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/AdFitSDK\/documentation\/AdFitSDK"]]},"references":{"doc://AdFitSDK/documentation/AdFitSDK/NativeAd":{"title":"Native 광고 연동","url":"